data.description: Remodeled home on 2.41 acres with plenty of new features and finishes including fresh paint, complete kitchen & bath updating, stainless steel appliances & all new tile/or vinyl plank flooring just to name a few.  Enjoy the screened-in porch and custom-built storage building!  The house is close to downtown Liberty Hill and minutes from 183A, Parmer Lane, shopping in Georgetown & Leander. Your kids will attend the acclaimed LHISD school system. Bring your horses and chickens with plenty of room to roam!
